parameters: The day the rain started to drizzle.

With the rhythm of raindrops hitting the leaves, I also
started to feel a bit sentimental.

As I watched the raindrops hitting the leaves and
falling, I looked up at the dark clouds from under the
tree.
The nostalgia of the past begins to float up thickly.
Direct from the source! A sudden charge!
There's a monument... Is it a memorial?

The erosion is so bad that I can't tell what's written on
the monument.
I feel like I saw something scary...
Direct from the source! A sudden charge!
Hikaru! What were you doing with Chika earlier?

When it comes to rumors, Kanae from the student council
appears!
Hikaru's vision went completely dark in front of him!
Hey, is this like a "Guess Who?" kind of thing?
At least pretend to be troubled for a bit.

Kanae released the hand that was covering my eyes like that
and lightly kicked the ground as if complaining.

The lingering scent of her that still remains in the air
was the fragrance of the perfume I used to wear back in
middle school.
I can vaguely see something like a small box.
I can vaguely see something like a small box.

So, the purpose of this ladder was for climbing up
here...

It seems like they couldn't come back down after dropping
the ladder.
I can't believe there's a place like this~
Hey Hikaru, isn't this place really beautiful?
What?! I told you to say the subject~

I think flowers can also be considered vegetables, don't
you think?
No, it definitely looks like a poisonous mushroom.

Hmm... yes, you're right. There's no need to deliberately try
it.
But, if it's just a little... hmm, what should we do?
I don't think it looks like food at all.
I don't think it looks like food at all.
